  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fend Off Hordes</h2>Being sent off-world for munitions testing is never a great assignment. Even more so when your destination turns out to be the zombie-infested halls of Caleme Castle. Batten down the hatches or get out and use your legs, corporate doesn't care. As long as you survive long enough for them to collect enough data, they'll be happy (that is, if they even feel emotion).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/1cf66df37dad9716f01cc49130e0388f.poster.avif?t=1717556324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/1cf66df37dad9716f01cc49130e0388f.webm?t=1717556324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/1cf66df37dad9716f01cc49130e0388f.mp4?t=1717556324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Empower Your Bullets</h2>While you are enjoying your limited stay at \"Zombie Manor\", you'll come across a great deal of gems. These empower your bullets, giving them all-around splendid effects such as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bone-chilling frostburn<br></li><li> Noxious gas<br></li><li> Piercing hot cinders<br></li><li> Immobilizing gunk<br></li><li> and much, much more!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/aca7a88489d7ee04aa19f082fe6b079e.poster.avif?t=1717556324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/aca7a88489d7ee04aa19f082fe6b079e.webm?t=1717556324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306780/extras/aca7a88489d7ee04aa19f082fe6b079e.mp4?t=1717556324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover New Builds</h2>There's a great deal of purchasing, selling, rerolling, and combining to get to. So what are you waiting on? Get to finding those rare item synergies and special gem combinations.",
